{"pageid":223125,"pagename":"Tome of the sun","title":"Tome of the sun","displaytitle":"Tome of the sun","revid":14265854,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png"},{"name":"description","value":"The tome of the sun is a book obtained during the miniquest In Search of Knowledge by searching the Temple Library bookshelves within the Forthos Dungeon. Initially empty, players must fill four Tattered sun pages that are received as drops from monsters within the dungeon."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-item\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-header\">Tome of the sun</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-image inventory-image infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/File:Tome_of_the_sun.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tome of the sun.png\" src=\"/images/Tome_of_the_sun.png?632be\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Released</th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/4_July\" title=\"4 July\">4 July</a> <a href=\"/w/2019\" title=\"2019\">2019</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Forthos_Dungeon\" title=\"Update:Forthos Dungeon\">Update</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Also called</th><td colspan=\"13\">Teachings of Ralos</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Quest_items\" title=\"Quest items\">Quest item</a></th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/In_Search_of_Knowledge\" title=\"In Search of Knowledge\">In Search of Knowledge</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Properties</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Items#Tradeability\" title=\"Items\">Tradeable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Worn_Equipment\" title=\"Worn Equipment\">Equipable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Stackable_items\" title=\"Stackable items\">Stackable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Choose_Option\" title=\"Choose Option\">Options</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Read, Check</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Destroy\" title=\"Destroy\">Destroy</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">You can reclaim another one from the Forthos Dungeon Library.</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Examine\" title=\"Examine\">Examine</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Ancient literature detailing the religion of Ralos.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Values</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Value\" title=\"Value\">Value</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">1 coin</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/High_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"High Level Alchemy\">High alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Low_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"Low Level Alchemy\">Low alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">Weight</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">1 kg</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Item ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">23506</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tome of the sun detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png/150px-Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png?24e2a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"159\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png/225px-Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png?24e2a 1.5x, /images/thumb/Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png/300px-Tome_of_the_sun_detail.png?24e2a 2x\" data-file-width=\"1366\" data-file-height=\"1447\" /></a></div>\n<p>The <b>tome of the sun</b> is a book obtained during the <a href=\"/w/Miniquest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Miniquest\">miniquest</a> <a href=\"/w/In_Search_of_Knowledge\" title=\"In Search of Knowledge\">In Search of Knowledge</a> by searching the Temple Library bookshelves within the <a href=\"/w/Forthos_Dungeon\" title=\"Forthos Dungeon\">Forthos Dungeon</a>. Initially empty, players must fill four <a href=\"/w/Tattered_sun_page\" title=\"Tattered sun page\">Tattered sun pages</a> that are received as drops from monsters within the dungeon.\n</p><p>The tome contains the teachings of <a href=\"/w/Ralos\" title=\"Ralos\">Ralos</a>, the god of the sun.\n</p><p>If lost, it can be reclaimed from the southeastern bookshelves in the Temple Library, or from a <a href=\"/w/Bookcase\" title=\"Bookcase\">bookcase</a> within a <a href=\"/w/Player-owned_house\" title=\"Player-owned house\">player-owned house</a> if the tome has been fully restored.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transcript\">Transcript</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Tome_of_the_sun?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Transcript\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Tome_of_the_sun?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Transcript\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div><div class=\"seealso\">The following text is transcluded from <a href=\"/w/Transcript:Tome_of_the_sun\" title=\"Transcript:Tome of the sun\">Transcript:Tome of the sun</a>.</div><div class=\"transcript\">\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;font-size:17px\">Origin of Ralos</div><hr />\n<p>The world was nothing and began when Ralos came into being. With a burst of glorious energy which provides us with heat, light and from this, life. The power of the sun is rivaled by none. We are blessed to receive it's glory during the day and we lament that we are not worthy during the night. Praise the sun.\n</p>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;font-size:17px\">Tenets of Ralos</div><hr />\n<p>We must strive to be like Ralos during our lives. To be bold, honest, bright and brimming with positive energy. To seize opportunities, to regret not the past and to live life to the fullest. To fully commit ourselves to our goals during the daylight hours and then recuperate our lost energy during the night.\n</p>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;font-size:17px\">Following Ralos pt.1</div><hr />\n<p>To emulate Ralos is to spread your own positive energy to as many people as possible. To provide them with sustenance, support and warmth both physically and emotionally. Ralos does so without regard for who they are or what they believe in without discrimination and as should we.\n</p>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;font-size:17px\">Following Ralos pt.2</div><hr />\nAs followers of Ralos we must strive to work against those who would consume the world in darkness, those who would spread cold and negative emotions to others and harm their fellow man for to do so is to become less human. However, do not hate your enemy, lest hatred becomes you, instead take pity on those that cannot see the light and do your best to guide them towards it.</div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Tome_of_the_sun?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Tome_of_the_sun?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"11 July 2019\"><a href=\"/w/11_July\" title=\"11 July\">11&#160;July</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2019\" title=\"2019\">2019</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Last_Man_Standing_Beta_and_Splashing_Restrictions\" title=\"Update:Last Man Standing Beta and Splashing Restrictions\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Typos within the tome, as well as when checking pages, were fixed.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"In Search of Knowledge\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:In_Search_of_Knowledge\" title=\"Template:In Search of Knowledge\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:In_Search_of_Knowledge\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:In_Search_of_Knowledge?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit